show.description: 4 YouTubers with expertise in supernatural events are seeking recognition from the audience whilst solving a Case: the spirit that haunts the schools' bathroom in Brazil. As they investigate, their staged scares turn into real horrors. Trapped between skepticism and the supernatural, they must uncover the truth before they become the next victims of the cursed entity.
